snippet.title: SUPER World of Goo Trailer | World of Goo Demake in Pico-8
snippet.description:
Discord - https://discord.com/invite/jRkuQh2nr8
play it here - https://virtuavirtues-backlog.itch.io/super-world-of-goo-demo
project file for modding - https://www.lexaloffle.com/bbs/?tid=142393
trailer music by Archonic - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G10fCx2UyRw

"A demake of World of Goo in Pico-8, a physics puzzler where you build giant towers of goo to reach dusty metal pipes."
